{
  "stem": "13471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when-- when Truman had sent out this message saying all US government agencies will cooperate, a lot of people used this as an excuse to get rid of their no-goods and has-beens and want-to-get-rid-ofs and so forth.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we got there, Dostert and I realized very quickly we were gonna have to send a lot of these people right straight back home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were useless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I got this boy in there, Wallie Cohn, who was Jewish, and whose father had been in one of those [INAUDIBLE] towns.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've forgotten which.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And had fled in good time, got his family out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But Wallie didn't have a good education in Germany or in-- or in the United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He spoke English and German, but both of a very rudimentary kind, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he wouldn't do for an interpreter or a translator at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was going-- running them down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is about four or five days after Wallie had appeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I called him into my office, and I said, Wallie, I guess you know what this is all about.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, you just can't cut the mustard as an either interpreter or as a translator, and we've got to send you home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I had put all these people that were to be sent home in a special assembly point which they called Siberia, you see.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he says, oh, don't send me to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't send me to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, well, why not?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, have you got a car?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, is it in good shape?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, no, it's in terrible shape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, let me have it for three days, huh?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
